    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold strictly as-is. It currently has significant mechanical issues, including an engine that runs roughly and a transmission that slips, meaning it will likely need a tow. The body shows heavy wear with noticeable rust patches, deep scratches, and a faded finish, while the interior requires a complete overhaul due to extensive stains and tears. This would be an ideal purchase for someone looking for a major restoration project or a donor vehicle for parts.",
